
Setting breakpoints:
  • `bp`
  • `bu`
  • `bm`

Listing breakpoints:
  • `bl`

{ Adding a command to a breakpoint

  The following example uses the → Windows/development/Debugging/tools/commands/d[`da`] comamnd to print the string that `*esp+8` points at.
code {
bp 0x76265f20 "da poi(esp+8); gc"
code }

}
